# HEMS Mosquitto ACL File
# Per-service topic permissions — principle of least privilege
#
# Format:
#   user <username>
#   topic [read|write|readwrite] <topic_pattern>
#
# Run infra/mosquitto/setup-users.sh to (re)generate the passwd file.

# --- Brain service ---
# Needs full read on office/# and hems/# to receive sensor data,
# and write on mcp/# to send device commands.
user hems-brain
topic readwrite office/#
topic readwrite hems/#
topic readwrite mcp/#

# --- Backend API service ---
# Reads sensor/event data, publishes task reports to office/# topics.
user hems-backend
topic read   office/#
topic read   hems/#
topic write  office/+/task_report/#

# --- Voice service ---
# No MQTT pub/sub needed (REST only), but subscribe to voice commands if needed.
user hems-voice
topic read   hems/brain/#

# --- HA Bridge ---
# Publishes home device state to hems/home/#.
# No need to subscribe (brain subscribes).
user hems-ha-bridge
topic write  hems/home/#
topic read   hems/home/bridge/status

# --- Biometric Bridge ---
# Publishes biometric readings to hems/personal/biometrics/#.
user hems-biometric
topic write  hems/personal/biometrics/#

# --- GAS Bridge ---
# Publishes Google data to hems/gas/#.
user hems-gas
topic write  hems/gas/#

# --- Obsidian Bridge ---
# Publishes note changes to hems/personal/notes/#.
user hems-obsidian
topic write  hems/personal/notes/#

# --- localcraw Bridge ---
# Publishes PC metrics to hems/pc/# and service status to hems/services/#.
user hems-localcraw
topic write  hems/pc/#
topic write  hems/services/#

# --- Perception service ---
# Publishes camera/activity data to office/+/camera/# and office/+/activity/#.
user hems-perception
topic write  office/+/camera/#
topic write  office/+/activity/#
topic write  hems/perception/#

# --- IoT sensor devices (zone sensors, MCP agents) ---
# Sensors publish to office/{zone}/sensor/# and respond on mcp/+/response/#.
# Use a shared credential for all IoT devices.
user hems-iot
topic write  office/#
topic write  mcp/+/response/#
topic read   mcp/#
